 Solemn ceremony marks Handover A solemn, historic ceremony has marked the resumption of the exercise of sovereignty over Hong Kong by the People's Republic of China. His Royal Highness The Prince of Wales and the President of the People's Republic of China (PRC) HE Mr Jiang Zemin both spoke at the ceremony, which straddled midnight of June 30 and July 1. The ceremony was telecast live around the world. 
